title: #163:  Clinton Global Initiative with the Propaganda Report's BJ Binkly and Monica Perez
description:
Thank you so much for the tuning in for another Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from the Propaganda Report Podcast, BJ Binkly and Monica Perez, to discuss the long list of the Clinton's connections to the Dark Arts! Thank you so much for your support and please enjoy the show.
